{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/meets3to1","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"meets3to1","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Foundations"}],"externalID":"s:15OUDSFoundations15OUDSWCAG21RatioV9meets3to1Sbvp","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"meets3to1","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","title":"meets3to1"},"abstract":[{"text":"If the computed contrast ratio between two given colors meets the 3:1 requirement","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio\/meets3to1"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Some countries set up new laws so as to force companies to have a better accessibility of their digital services.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is for example the case for France with the "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"also named “RGAA”.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron).","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This utility helps to define whether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"See for example ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"ic_layers.png":{"identifier":"ic_layers.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSFoundations\/ic_layers.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio/meets3to1":{"kind":"symbol","title":"meets3to1","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio\/meets3to1","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/meets3to1","abstract":[{"text":"If the computed contrast ratio between two given colors meets the 3:1 requirement","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"meets3to1"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":